      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>Your nanites can redirect energy back at your foes. When you would take energy damage, you can spend a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.vh6n0Ad3lamOJXpV]{Nanite Surge (Ex)} as a reaction to reduce that damage by your nanocyte level, having nanites contain the energy instead. The first time you damage a creature with an unarmed strike or weapon that targets EAC on your next turn, you can increase the damage dealt by the amount of damage you absorbed with this ability. This damage is the same type as the prevented damage.</p>"
